latestPosts.caption:
Superfine :  Tailoring Black Style  black dandyism  tailored for you  While focusing on the theme ,we wanted to focus on  Ms. Hill’s silhouettes ,  while adding @cheneychanofficial silhouettes for collaboration.  Regal ! In one word , is where she wanted to live .
  The silhouettes were the most important aspect.
The fabric was a key element in bringing the whimsy of the dandy as well as tailoring.
The halo detail elevated the look.  Bring you regal encompassing Ms. Lauryn Hill legacy to the culture.
With just 7 days to create this majestic moment .  I spent hours on the phone and on international calls with the design team .  If 7 days got you this.
Imagine having 7 months to prepare and design for @metgalaofficial_ .  Thank you @cheneychanofficial  for making this moment happen for Ms. Hill and myself. When I say a moment, this has been that .  1. History was made .  2. I think the carpet was perfect for this moment.  3. The grace kelly as a briefcase.  4. I had 30 mins to cut this afro.  5. If anyone would have told me 15 years ago before signing on to this job ,that I would make history by collaborating with  Ms. Lauryn Hill on hair/wardrobe .
Forever grateful ❤️ Thank you  suit @cheneychanofficial  jewelry @emefacolejewellery  @smo.gold  watch  @hublot  bag @hermes  shoes @marcjacobs.  Producer @alexnrivas
